<p>Have you tried moving your logic/code for figuring out which side you are closest to into that method?</p>
<p>Something along the lines of…</p>
<pre><code class="lang-auto">public Pose2d getDesiredPose () {
    Pose2d currentPose = poseEstimator.getEstimatedPosition();
    double distanceToLeft = currentPose.getTranslation().getDistance(FieldPoses.kCoralBlueLeft.getTranslation());
    double distanceToRight = currentPose.getTranslation().getDistance(FieldPoses.kCoralBlueRight.getTranslation());

	if (distanceToLeft &lt; distanceToRight) {
    	return FieldPoses.kCoralBlueLeft;
    }
    else {
        return FieldPoses.kCoralBlueRight;
    }
}
</code></pre>
<p>Again, hope this helps!!</p>","post_number":5,"post_type":1,"posts_count":10,"updated_at":"2025-02-20T14:36:14.363Z","reply_count":1,"reply_to_post_number":4,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":5,"reads":76,"readers_count":75,"score":45.2,"yours":false,"topic_id":492381,"topic_slug":"pathplanner-pathfinding-while-button-is-pressed-in-tele-op","display_username":"Martin Nemaric","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":true,"can_wiki":false,"read":true,"user_title":null,"reply_to_user":{"id":73610,"username":"daniel3","name":"","avatar_template":"/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/d/a4c791/{size}.png"},"bookmarked":false,"actions_summary":[],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":56673,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":true,"wiki":false,"post_url":"/t/pathplanner-pathfinding-while-button-is-pressed-in-tele-op/492381/5","custom_user_title":null,"reactions":[],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":0,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null},{"id":3534109,"name":"","username":"daniel3","avatar_template":"/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/d/a4c791/{size}.png","created_at":"2025-02-20T15:02:00.287Z","cooked":"<p>We did this just to check if the pathfinding was working correctly, but once we fix the issue with the pathfinding trajectory, we’ll focus on the logic behind where it should go.</p>","post_number":6,"post_type":1,"posts_count":10,"updated_at":"2025-02-20T15:02:00.287Z","reply_count":1,"reply_to_post_number":5,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":62,"readers_count":61,"score":17.4,"yours":false,"topic_id":492381,"topic_slug":"pathplanner-pathfinding-whil